-No. No.

1:12:29.997 --> 1:12:33.174
You won't have to visit
because

1:12:33.218 --> 1:12:34.480
I'm not going.

1:12:38.005 --> 1:12:39.572
You-you didn't get in?

1:12:42.619 --> 1:12:43.576
I didn't apply.

1:12:47.014 --> 1:12:49.103
I... I don't understand.

1:12:50.888 --> 1:12:51.845
Yeah, you wouldn't.

1:12:55.066 --> 1:12:56.023
I could try.

1:12:57.590 --> 1:12:59.679
I mean...

1:12:59.723 --> 1:13:03.596
I know you don't like talking
about feelings and shit, but...

1:13:05.032 --> 1:13:06.512
I wanna understand.

1:13:08.775 --> 1:13:13.867
