baby Bea for a long time

1:13:27.228 --> 1:13:29.883
without any help from you.

1:13:32.233 --> 1:13:36.150
So, maybe, because...

1:13:36.194 --> 1:13:38.283
you do everything for them

1:13:38.326 --> 1:13:41.112
you've convinced yourself
that they're helpless.

1:13:43.027 --> 1:13:44.637
So...

1:13:44.681 --> 1:13:46.857
maybe, going to school

1:13:46.900 --> 1:13:48.641
is actually what's best
for everyone.

1:13:51.078 --> 1:13:52.036
