too...

1:14:02.568 --> 1:14:03.917
if you ever need me to.

1:14:07.617 --> 1:14:09.706
-Well, what do you mean?
-I don't know.

1:14:11.838 --> 1:14:13.492
Like, if you got sick again
or something.

1:14:19.585 --> 1:14:20.760
Um...

1:14:23.937 --> 1:14:26.374
I'm not gonna get
sick again.

1:14:26.418 --> 1:14:29.029
No, no, I don't...
I don't think that you will.

1:14:29.073 --> 1:14:31.510
I'm just saying that
if you did, I would...

1:14:31.554 --> 1:14:32.511
you know, be here.

1:14:39.562 --> 1:14:42.260
What kind of fucked up
fantasy is that, Bea?

1:14:42.303 --> 1:14:45.306
Wait. Why are you getting mad?

1:14:45.350 --> 1:14:48.832
