you want my cancer to come back.

1:14:48.875 --> 1:14:52.531
I... I didn't say that.
I didn't say that.

1:14:52.575 --> 1:14:56.535
You know, I wake up
every morning scared.

1:14:56.579 --> 1:15:00.539
So scared that sometimes
I can't even get out of bed.

1:15:00.583 --> 1:15:04.500
Because my first thought is,
what if I get sick again?

1:15:04.543 --> 1:15:09.374
So, you're here
just secretly hoping I do...

1:15:09.417 --> 1:15:12.159
Because what?

1:15:12.203 --> 1:15:14.422
Then people will have another
reason to feel bad for you?

1:15:14.466 --> 1:15:16.816
Because poor Bea.

1:15:16.860 --> 1:15:18.818
She's the only one
with problems.

1:15:18.862 --> 1:15:21.038
I'm not the only one
with problems.

1:15:22.648 --> 1:15:24.998
You act like it.

1:15:25.042 --> 1:15:27.871
Do you think I like people
pitying me?

1:15:27.914 --> 1:15:29.873
I think you like

1:15:29.916 --> 1:15:31.918
that you're smarter
than your parents.

1:15:31.962 --> 1:15:33.659
That way you get to be
in charge.

1:15:33.703 --> 1:15:35.139
And, I think you're scared

1:15:35.182 --> 1:15:36.532
to go to school because then you

1:15:36.575 --> 1:15:37.837
won't have anyone
to push around.

1:15:37.881 --> 1:15:39.447
Fuck you!

1:15:39.491 --> 1:15:41.580
You know, you can use your
parents as an excuse

1:15:41.624 --> 1:15:43.800
not to leave, but you're not
going to use me as one.

1:15:43.843 --> 1:15:45.932
Wha... Where are you going?

1:15:45.976 --> 1:15:48.326
I fought really hard
to have a future.

1:15:48.369 --> 1:15:51.242
So, it's really messed up

1:15:51.285 --> 1:15:53.549
when I see someone
throwing theirs away.

1:15:53.592 --> 1:15:56.377
And, I just
can't be part of that.

1:15:56.421 --> 1:15:57.378
What is that supposed to...

1:15:58.641 --> 1:16:00.077
Are you breaking up with me?

1:16:06.126 --> 1:16:11.262
♪ Do you want me for me

1:16:11.305 --> 1:16:15.179
♪ Or make believe

1:16:15.222 --> 1:16:17.964
♪ Rip me at the seams

1:16:18.008 --> 1:16:20.184
♪ Fill me

1:16:20.227 --> 1:16:25.363
♪ Full of your dreams

1:16:25.406 --> 1:16:30.847
♪ No I can't be
somebody else for you ♪♪

1:16:37.157 --> 1:16:38.550
Not much of an appetite, huh?

1:16:40.726 --> 1:16:41.684
I'm Mary.

1:16:44.425 --> 1:16:45.383
I know.

1:16:46.253 --> 1:16:48.081
Nia told me about you.

1:16:48.125 --> 1:16:51.345
And... No, I-I don't...

1:16:51.389 --> 1:16:54.435
know what happened to Bea.

1:16:54.479 --> 1:16:57.221
Oh, I'm not saying you do,
but it does seem strange that

1:16:57.264 --> 1:16:59.658
you haven't been in
to see her yet.

1:16:59.702 --> 1:17:00.616
Why is that?

1:17:02.748 --> 1:17:05.316
I just don't think she'd want me
seeing her like that.

1:17:13.280 --> 1:17:15.282
How'd you get in my house?

1:17:15.326 --> 1:17:18.764
I climbed the rain gutter
and snuck in through the window.

1:17:18.808 --> 1:17:20.418
-Really?
-No.

1:17:20.461 --> 1:17:23.682
-Your mom let me in.
-What're you doing here?

1:17:23.726 --> 1:17:25.249
You weren't answering my calls.

1:17:25.292 --> 1:17:27.294
It's because
I'm not talking to you.

1:17:27.338 --> 1:17:29.732
Well, you're talking to me now.

1:17:29.775 --> 1:17:31.951
I'm kinda busy right now, so...

1:17:31.995 --> 1:17:33.823
Right.

1:17:33.866 --> 1:17:35.694
Right, um...

1:17:35.738 --> 1:17:37.043
sorry.

1:17:39.742 --> 1:17:41.831
I came to apologize.

1:17:43.789 --> 1:17:46.966
-I was being an asshole.
-Yes. You were.

1:17:47.010 --> 1:17:48.011
A stupid asshole.

1:17:51.318 --> 1:17:53.190
I'm sorry that was so mean.

1:17:53.233 --> 1:17:55.758
Oh, my God,
I was being the asshole.

1:17:55.801 --> 1:17:57.368
Me.

1:17:57.411 --> 1:17:58.891
So let me apologize.

1:18:00.632 --> 1:18:03.069
I'm sorry, Nia.

1:18:03.113 --> 1:18:07.726
You're my best friend and I
shouldn't push you around.

1:18:07.770 --> 1:18:08.945
Especially
when I'm telling you

1:18:08.988 --> 1:18:10.729
not to let other people
push you around.

1:18:10.773 --> 1:18:12.557
I ju... I...

1:18:12.600 --> 1:18:14.428
I was so worried
we'd never talk again.

1:18:14.472 --> 1:18:16.430
I almost got an ulcer,
and I had to see a specialist.

1:18:16.474 --> 1:18:17.431
Oh, my God.

1:18:18.868 --> 1:18:20.696
So... tell me everything.

1:18:20.739 --> 1:18:22.741
How many times did you
and Ethan do it this week?

1:18:22.785 --> 1:18:23.699
Like...

1:18:25.439 --> 1:18:26.919
Twenty!

1:18:26.963 --> 1:18:28.834
What prom dress
did you end up picking?

1:18:28.878 --> 1:18:30.140
Oh, um...

1:18:32.055 --> 1:18:33.230
Yeah, I'm not going.

1:18:33.273 --> 1:18:34.535
Was it because
I said you look slutty?

1:18:34.579 --> 1:18:36.320
Because, I meant good slutty?

1:18:38.322 --> 1:18:40.106
No.

1:18:40.150 --> 1:18:42.935
I... I think
Ethan and I broke up.

1:18:42.979 --> 1:18:45.329
What?! Why?

1:18:45.372 --> 1:18:48.724
It's kind of a long story,
and I was...

1:18:48.767 --> 1:18:50.987
hoping I could maybe just
talk about it over pancakes

1:18:51.030 --> 1:18:52.075
if you wanna...
I don't know,

1:18:52.118 --> 1:18:53.903
just like go to IHOP
and hang.

1:18:53.946 --> 1:18:55.078
