1:18:57.036 --> 1:18:58.908
-You are.
-Andy and Esther broke up.

1:18:58.951 --> 1:19:00.910
And then he asked me, but...

1:19:00.953 --> 1:19:03.216
Screw it.
Hos before bros.

1:19:03.260 --> 1:19:06.002
What? No...
I mean, I-I-I know I said

1:19:06.045 --> 1:19:08.178
I'd stopped telling you
what to do, but...

1:19:08.221 --> 1:19:11.181
You're going to that
stupid prom.

1:19:11.224 --> 1:19:14.010
What if Andy asked me
as a joke?

1:19:14.053 --> 1:19:16.055
