-Bea, I'm serious.
-Nia, you look beautiful.

1:19:40.645 --> 1:19:42.516
I feel bad leaving you.

1:19:42.560 --> 1:19:46.042
Don't. Don't. I've got...

1:19:46.085 --> 1:19:49.045
tons of, tons of stuff t-to do.

1:19:49.959 --> 1:19:52.483
I just have to do.

1:19:52.526 --> 1:19:55.181
I wasn't just sad.

1:19:55.225 --> 1:19:56.182
I was mad...

1:19:58.402 --> 1:20:00.534
at Ethan, my parents.

1:20:03.146 --> 1:20:04.321
But, mostly at myself.

1:20:07.628 --> 1:20:10.022
I let myself
buy into the fantasy.

1:20:11.415 --> 1:20:12.851
And now it was gone.

1:20:14.766 --> 1:20:19.249
♪ I hold my head up
just enough to see the sky... ♪

1:20:19.292 --> 1:20:21.251
I figured Disney was the only
way I was getting

1:20:21.294 --> 1:20:22.861
to California anytime soon.

1:20:22.905 --> 1:20:25.995
♪ We'll put up such a fight

1:20:26.038 --> 1:20:31.391
♪ When they fade into the
dust and into ash ♪

1:20:31.435 --> 1:20:37.006
♪ And when the tide it comes
you will float above ♪

1:20:37.049 --> 1:20:42.533
♪ And you will be
one day exactly what you are ♪

