1:21:15.479 --> 1:21:17.698
Oh! Oh, shit!

1:21:17.742 --> 1:21:19.787
Shit! Shit! Shit!

1:21:21.267 --> 1:21:22.355
So...

1:21:25.010 --> 1:21:27.665
Finally doing with all that
high school bullshit.

1:21:27.708 --> 1:21:28.753
Hey!

1:21:33.279 --> 1:21:34.237
I'll buy a ticket.

1:21:37.893 --> 1:21:39.807
-We're out.
