-Selling raffle tickets?
-Celine Dion!

1:21:46.553 --> 1:21:49.948
-How much... Celine Dion?
-Yes. Celine Dion.

1:21:51.384 --> 1:21:52.733
So, what are you guys
up to tonight?

1:21:52.777 --> 1:21:54.822
-Damien?
-Uh...

1:21:54.866 --> 1:21:56.999
