tonight, man.

1:21:57.042 --> 1:21:59.088
-You're welcome.
-Hello!

1:21:59.131 --> 1:22:00.785
Hmm.

1:22:00.828 --> 1:22:04.876
This is a nice... Aw.
This's my mom's favorite song.

1:22:04.920 --> 1:22:06.747
-There you go.
-Turn it up.

1:22:06.791 --> 1:22:08.619
♪ Alright alright!

1:22:08.662 --> 1:22:11.578
♪ Hey!

1:22:11.622 --> 1:22:14.668
Uh, my...
This's a nice car.

1:22:14.712 --> 1:22:17.933
It's a really nice car,
my boyfriend, uh...

1:22:17.976 --> 1:22:19.935
My... Well, my ex-boyfriend,
would've liked,

1:22:19.978 --> 1:22:21.719
would've liked this car.

1:22:21.762 --> 1:22:24.548
I was so...
He was still my boyfriend.

1:22:24.591 --> 1:22:26.898
-His loss.
-No, no, I... I don't know.

1:22:26.942 --> 1:22:28.247
♪ Hold up hold up

1:22:28.291 --> 1:22:30.815
-This is his song.
-This second song?

1:22:30.858 --> 1:22:33.513
♪ Oh no think I need
a break I got conscience ♪

1:22:33.557 --> 1:22:36.168
Lighten up,
have a drink with me.

