Hey, bro.
Could you not drink back there?

1:22:38.779 --> 1:22:41.521
-I just got my license back.
-Where else are we gonna drink?

1:22:43.219 --> 1:22:45.264
Besides...

1:22:45.308 --> 1:22:47.266
-I like the back seat.
